Shut Up and Listen!						KEY:Evangelist Boon ~ Hadregash ~ Shut Up and Listen!		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Faith Based Boon.SpecialQuality.Supernatural		SOURCEPAGE:p.77		DESC:If you have performed your daily obedience, you may, as a standard action, provide an adjacent ally with similar guidance with a soft-spoken word or two. Your ally gains a +2 circumstance bonus on attack and damage rolls for 1 round; this bonus increases to +4 for dirty trick combat maneuver attempts. You can use this ability %1 times per day.|CHA
