My Might Is Mighty!						KEY:Sentinel Boon ~ Hadregash ~ My Might Is Mighty!		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Faith Based Boon.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary		SOURCEPAGE:p.77		DESC:If you have performed your daily obedience, three times per day as a move action, you can gain the benefits of a combat feat you dont have for the following minute. You must meet all the feats prerequisites, and if you use this ability again before the duration expires, the new combat feat replaces the old one. If a combat feat has a daily use limitation (such as Stunning Fist), any uses of that combat feat while using this ability count toward that feats daily limit, even through multiple uses of this ability. 
